  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b85\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The whole country is on the verge of stagnation without fuel - Anura Kumara",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is doubtful whether the ship, which was not booked on the basis of a formal bid, will arrive at the Port of Colombo.",
        "Anura Kumara Dissanayake, leader of the National People's Force, said the country was on the verge of stagnation.",
        "He said this while addressing a conference held in Jaffna on Saturday (25).",
        "The Minister of Power and Energy said last week that the fuel ships would arrive in the country on the 23rd and 24th.",
        "No ship arrived in the country. At present the ship has crossed the Sri Lankan border into the Krishnapatnam area.",
        "The ship that arrived in Sri Lanka is currently in India. This is not a shipwreck based on the appropriate bid.",
        "The ship, which was spotted in the Mediterranean by emergency importers, was thus summoned. It is highly doubtful whether the ship will come to Sri Lanka or not.",
        "So the whole country is on the brink of stagnation. Bonds have been obtained from a bank in the United States.",
        "They expire on July 18th. As such, the government has declared that it will not be able to repay the loan. The US Reserve Bank has filed a lawsuit against the government over this.",
        "The case alleges that the Rajapaksa family looted people's property. They are also said to be hidden in tax-exempt countries such as the Seychelles.",
        "The lawsuit was probably funded by Japan's Hiroshima and Nagasaki. Economists have predicted that.",
        "They have created a hopeless situation regarding the future of the youth. Farmers, fishermen, government services are all paralyzed. It has also decided to close intermittent schools. What country is this? Don't we have to change this?",
        "Shouldn't the rulers be responsible for this? This is not a natural disaster. This is not a disaster caused by floods or hurricanes. He said that all should work together without any discrimination to remove the rulers who have put the country in this situation."
      ],
